headline: Why onsemi (ON) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of analog chips maker onsemi (NASDAQ:ON) jumped 4.9% in the morning session after a wave of positive sentiment boosted the semiconductor sector as chip giant Nvidia announced a major partnership with Intel.
